Things to note: 

1. It asks for a cd for me, and as someone suggested, just move the setup folder off the iso to your desktop and launch with the iso mounted and it's fine.

2. illustrator does not have its amtlib.dll file in its main directory (Program Files\Adobe\Illustrator\), one of the text documents in the crack folder says its real directory

3. if you are new, yes, it comes with a keygen, it's on the iso file in the "activation" folder

Everything works, so far, except for Adobe Acrobat X Pro... on my machine.

and the Photoshop that comes with it isn't the Extended version, unlike what Adobe has advertised.
If this isn't much of an issue to you, then you're good to go with this torrent.
For those who might want the Acrobat and Photoshop Extended, or who got this working, help please. Thank you.
